name: Manulife Multifactor U.S. Small Cap Index ETF
longDescription: Manulife Multifactor U.S. Small Cap Index ETF seeks to replicate to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses the performance of the John Hancock Dimensional Small Cap Index CAD Hedged or any successor thereto. Manulife Multifactor U.S. Small Cap Index ETF invests directly or indirectly primarily in small capitalization U.S. equities. The ETF invests directly or indirectly primarily in small capitalization US equities.
